{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi360 
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 5}Sarai complained to Abram, \uc1\u8220*May the wrong I suffer be on you! I myself gave my slave-girl to you; and now that she sees that she has conceived, I am despised by her; may the {\scaps Lord} judge between me and you.\uc1\u8221*{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}But Abram said to Sarai, \uc1\u8220*Your maid-servant is in your power, do to her whatever seems right to you.\uc1\u8221* Then Sarai ill-treated her so that she fled from her presence.
